Basic
Extras

Lounge

Refrigerator, coffee maker, filtered drinking water, microwave, and the kitchen sink

Recreation Room

Foosball table, electronic drum, Xbox, Gaming PC with VR, dartboard, and modern video conferencing system

Resource Center

Canon image RUNNER ADVANCE 4245 copier/printer/scanner/finisher/fax and 3D printer

Conference Rooms

7-seat and 15-seat conference rooms, modern video conferencing system with wireless collaboration

Classroom

20-seat classroom with projector and Lectern

Discussion Room

Ideal Place for members to take calls or have small impromptu meetings

Member-only Events

Access to events exclusively offered to TIQC members

Campus Cultural Events

Members can participate in events offered by the college and its various organizations.

Event Space

Our event spaces can be rented out individually for nonmembers. Members also have the option of hosting their larger events in one of the Queens College campus event spaces.

Housing at the Summit

Access to Queens College’sSummit apartments

Campus Parking

Members are eligible to purchase on campus parking for the additional fee of $275/year

Gymnasium

Access to Queens Colleges FitzGerald gymnasium features pool, fitness center, indoor tennis court, etc.

*Additional charges may apply to some of the “Extras”. Please inquire to find out.

Host An Event

Thank you for your interest in hosting your meeting at the Tech Incubator @ Queens College!

All our conference rooms and our classroom are equipped with whiteboards and a professional conference system (HuddleCAM 3X 1080P camera, Phoenix USB Conference Phone, 60/70 smart LED TV, and Extron Sharelink Wireless Collaboration Gateway) to support your meetings.

If you have login credentials for our Meeting Room Booking System, please go ahead to book the meeting room you need. Otherwise, please fill out our inquiry form below or call 718-570-0573 to start planning your next event or meeting! You may check our space pictures.

We look forward to having you in our space!
